      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-zpx-trt-pvi       not  = w-exe-scg-zpv
                     go to exe-exp-zpx-200.
       exe-exp-zpx-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento numero records letti                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   inc-rec-let-000      thru inc-rec-let-999        .
           if        w-exe-flg-brk        not  = spaces
                     go to exe-exp-zpx-800.
       exe-exp-zpx-550.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
