      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-exe-ctr-002          .
       exe-exp-zpx-632.
           add       1                    to   w-exe-ctr-002          .
           if        w-exe-ctr-002        >    3
                     go to exe-exp-zpx-634.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
